-- Lynxiz --

Lynxiz frowns, she doesn't know anyone by the name of 
Panthro. "Panthro? How do you know my name? What faction do you 
represent?" Lynxiz walks away from the wreckage, "Lynxiz, maximize!" 
Her torso spins, her legs and arms fold, and she transforms into her 
sleek Lynx beast mode, padding towards the destination that she had 
been given. All the while, she was awaiting a reply.
